{"tid":1554191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港四等人制","createTime":"2019-09-09T01:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:35:27.000Z","uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a94053317542e9e676afdc100232eab4b49f3713","tid":1554191,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"有錢人》撐警/親中藍絲》香港人》年輕人<br />\n<br />\n話說尋日經過尖沙咀地鐵站<br />\n有一班防暴喺度<br />\n我衣著係深藍色衫+迪卡龍前線背囊+黑帽+黑長遮<br />\n我行過同啲防暴有幾下眼神接觸<br />\n都係掂行掂過<br />\n然後後面有個𡃁仔<br />\n剩係著黑衫 就比狗叫左埋去逗下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾無事放走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 80後<br />\n<br />\n好明顯<br />\n你個樣後生<br />\n就行過都錯<br />\n<br />\n上左年紀既啲狗唔敢亂咁拉<br />\n<br />\n所以街坊屌狗<br />\n你個樣好後生既話<br />\n就唔好玩咁夜同企咁前<br />\n因為啲狗專捉年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b4154afd7db6d7f831d861a4bece0dcf6a137d","tid":1554191,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc69793ec9b3df71618e2292cfae49d7bd9664fa","tid":1554191,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"琴日太子mtr入面都見到個靚仔巴打比成班狗又搜又摷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}